message.body: Watcha doing ?
Hey! Sorry I missed your call, I was thriftin in jp. I went to Harvard square for a bit too. I'm gonna head to your area in a minute so maybe I can meet you
when you're done class. Daniel missed his bus so he won't be in till later. How are you darlin?
Amelia I'm feeling so sick. I'm in class now.
I'm sorry! My phones gonna die, I'm right by your school, when will you be done?
630. Where are you ? You want to meet at Peets coffee at 645
Are you home yet Angie forgot her keys ...
I'm in Brookline, should I go back and give her keys?
No it's cool she just grabbed mine. I talked to Daniel
Are you home
How is he? Almost
He's fine
Don't worry are you ok
Angie will be home soon
They are in a hospital in the Bronx
Call me befor you leave my house
Take green to park street transfer to red line towards. Alewife for two stops
Hey lady! I just got back to philly. I'm picking up pizza for me and Daniel, he's ok, just super worn out and shaken up. Thank you so so much for showing me
such a wonderful time. It was so great being around you, you're a sweet beautiful special intelligent and amazing woman. I'm so proud of you and grateful to
have you as a friend. I can't wait to come back and visit. Just know how perfect you are. I love you.
I love you. I miss you already. I'm glad Daniel is ok.
